definitions.definition: Any of the species of Somateria spp. and Polysticta stelleri or of the seaduck subfamily Merginae , which line their nests with fine down (taken from their own bodies).

main_definition: Any of the species of Somateria spp. and Polysticta stelleri or of the seaduck subfamily Merginae , which line their nests with fine down (taken from their own bodies).
